{"tid":332851,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"日女2017最想睡的男星 福山雅治排名暴跌","createTime":"2017-07-23T10:07:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-26T11:35:49.000Z","uid":9573,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e0efa7a019935d0a0d00a97ca2fe2efdf5c33ccd","tid":332851,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T10:07:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2676/d2676031.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2676%2Fd2676031.jpg&h=8d186915&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日本雜誌《週刊女性》頗受歡迎的企劃「最想睡的男星」2017版出爐，第一名由《晝顏》中的小王齋藤工奪下，打敗羽生結弦、藤岡靛及木村拓哉。福山雅治則排名暴跌。<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2676/d2676032.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2676%2Fd2676032.jpg&h=03976ef6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《週刊女性》的這項企劃停了2年，今年再度舉辦，找了1200名成年日本女性調查，發表了百大排名。齋藤工上一次調查是第4名，這次奪冠，羽生結弦則是花式滑冰選手；藤岡靛則是由台灣「逆輸入」紅回日本，木村拓哉則由上一次的第2名掉到第4名。<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2676/d2676034.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2676%2Fd2676034.jpg&h=c5f86771&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2676/d2676033.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2676%2Fd2676033.jpg&h=cf3d6e68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n值得注意的是，福山雅治的排名一路下滑，不知是否受到2015年的婚訊影響，從2014年的第2名到如今的第10名。前10名的其它還有並列第7名的高橋一生、德井義實，第9名的長瀨智也等等。"},{"pid":"4647f4ed26ef2c33b62a6486283902bf427cd60d","tid":332851,"uid":126796,"like":39,"dislike":2,"score":37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T10:10:34.000Z","msg":"物化男性"},{"pid":"eb5f7503e039adaf8b715e20f750a132ffb2e4ed","tid":332851,"uid":37005,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T10:12:14.000Z","msg":"羽生結弦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1955963eba8031d1fd0ac0859ef11ac891d6301d","tid":332851,"uid":1403,"like":48,"dislike":1,"sco